org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.daos

Class AbstractDAO<T extends JPAAbstractEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.daos.AbstractDAO<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - class of entity, for which actions are performed.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AgentInfoDAO, BatchDAO, DataSetDAO, ExperimentDAO, ExternalAgentDAO, FileMappingDAO, ModelDAO, ResultDAO, RoleDAO, TaskTypeDAO, UserDAO, UserPriviledgeDAO

    public abstract class AbstractDAO<T extends JPAAbstractEntity>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class AbstractDAO contains general functions to manipulate with entities. These general functions are used by classes, that are inherited from this class, in functions specific to that particular entity.
